race.comment: Myriad of winning chances in an open race. POETS ARTISTRY (3) has been in sparkling form winning last two, the latest first try this trip. Was supposed to start earlier this month but was scratched at the barriers and has since trialled. Has the claim and a nice draw here and expected to measure up again. BALLON D'OR (1) led throughout to score last time. Has the claim again offsetting the weight and expected to give a sight. EN FLIQUE (13) was a close-up third fresh and strips fitter for the extra ground. Drops in weight, nice draw and placed 3/4 here at home. STRUMMER (10) is another local drawn for a soft run with cover. Worth including.
